      <title>摩根士丹利策略师认为通胀是股市走势的关键</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/morgan-stanley-s-wilson-sees-inflation-as-key-for-path-of-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利策略师表示，美国主要经济数据发出的“喜忧参半”的信息以及随之而来的股市波动意味着投资者应该买入必需消费品等防御性板块。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/morgan-stanley-s-wilson-sees-inflation-as-key-for-path-of-stocks</guid>
